@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_nufgpa(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.10 - v2 + 0.36)) + ((v2 + 0.73 / tmp + 0.19) / wp.exp(v0 + 0.30)))
    v0 = wp.exp(((v0 + 0.76 - v1 + 0.76) / wp.cos(v0 + 0.80)))
    v2 = v0
    v0 = wp.exp(((tmp + 0.46 * v0 + 0.03) - wp.cos(v0 + 0.09)))
    v2 = 0.78
    tmp = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.52 - tmp + 0.25)) + wp.exp((v1 + 0.45 / v2 + 0.79)))
    data[tid] = v0
